## MVVM Implementation Patterns

### 1. Model Layer
Keep models simple and focused on data representation.

```swift
struct User: Codable, Equatable {
    let id: Int
    let name: String
    let email: String
    let avatar: URL?
}

struct APIResponse<T: Codable>: Codable {
    let data: T
    let success: Bool
    let message: String?
}

enum LoadingState {
    case idle
    case loading
    case loaded
    case error(Error)
